{"id":28464,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":25}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"灯塔","column":"大众信箱,问答栏:","genre":"","count":"86","ytitle":"","mtitle":"失魂症","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"俊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新贵:据西医说，我患的是不治的心脏病。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中医:中医是不知道什么心脏病心炎病…的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新贵:那么我究竟患的是什么病呢?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中医:我断定是失魂症，而且是绝症呢!"}]}